    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soulbound Dream is an action game blending rogue-lite and puzzle elements. Explore dreams and nightmares to restore balance to Etherea. Use your emotions to modify your spells, defeat monsters, level up, and enhance your skills. Traverse these dreamlike worlds to unlock new spells and overcome the challenges that await </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/595816d320ed07d883ff011fa50968a6.avif?t=1728928652\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras_big/595816d320ed07d883ff011fa50968a6.avif?t=1728928652 width=800 height=242 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/f7f37a8b33a63192f809f15bf2b5685a.avif?t=1728928652\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras_big/f7f37a8b33a63192f809f15bf2b5685a.avif?t=1728928652 width=800 height=242 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Etherea was once a world of perfect balance, where dreams and nightmares coexisted in harmony, maintained by the Etherions, spiritual creatures bound to emotions. However, a mysterious force shattered this balance, strengthening the nightmares and plunging the world into chaos. The Guardians of Etherea, protectors of the realm, embarked on a desperate quest to understand and reverse this corruption. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Thane, a young guardian determined to restore balance by finding the legendary Balance of Etherea. Master your emotions to free lost souls and combat the darkness that is engulfing this once serene world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/8f92872dc6ceb404d98d129a2317c50d.avif?t=1728928652\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras_big/8f92872dc6ceb404d98d129a2317c50d.avif?t=1728928652 width=800 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  Unlock and master up to 8 unique emotions (4 available in the demo)! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/f325a616904100263aef131c2e527de5.poster.avif?t=1728928652\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/f325a616904100263aef131c2e527de5.webm?t=1728928652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                   Each emotion changes your skills and combat style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/32f960e2c65ba26c4c3fb5775e50b8ba.poster.avif?t=1728928652\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/32f960e2c65ba26c4c3fb5775e50b8ba.webm?t=1728928652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                             Progress through trials to find the Balance of Etherea!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/e2cbafdf06177a159fa53785b3857f53.poster.avif?t=1728928652\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/e2cbafdf06177a159fa53785b3857f53.webm?t=1728928652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                               Obtain new skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/1a43b6be819ee528f7a1418bbd6c7d0c.poster.avif?t=1728928652\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/1a43b6be819ee528f7a1418bbd6c7d0c.webm?t=1728928652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                               Fight corrupted entities to level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/30c6d5106e0aa3403ea9231463ad6d9b.poster.avif?t=1728928652\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/30c6d5106e0aa3403ea9231463ad6d9b.webm?t=1728928652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                        Upgrade your character and their emotional skills as you level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/477017f6cd31cbb8f6831f6367427127.poster.avif?t=1728928652\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/477017f6cd31cbb8f6831f6367427127.webm?t=1728928652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras/06b71b4effb42a78a3f2ae5450649687.avif?t=1728928652\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187740/extras_big/06b71b4effb42a78a3f2ae5450649687.avif?t=1728928652 width=800 height=159 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SoulBound Dream is a passion project that I'm developing on my own, with the goal of providing you with an immersive and enjoyable experience. This game is the result of my years of work in game development and represents a major turning point in my career. I left everything behind to make this dream a reality, and your support is essential to make this adventure come true. Thank you for being a part of this journey.</p>",
